mt_samples %>%
  unnest_tokens(word, transcription) %>%
  count(word) %>%
  top_n(20, n) %>%
  ggplot(aes(n, word)) +
  geom_col()

Based on the graph, most of the most common words are typical words used in plain language, such as and, in, and of. The only common word that was not this type of word was âpatientâ. This makes sense because of the context of the transcript.
